      <section eId="sec_3118">
        <num>3118</num>
        <heading>Demand for address of party or of person who possessed an assigned cause of action or defense</heading>
        <content>
          <p>  Rule 3118. Demand for address of party or of person who possessed an\nassigned cause of action or defense. A party may serve on any party a\nwritten notice demanding a verified statement setting forth the post\noffice address and residence of the party, of any specified officer or\nmember of the party and of any person who possessed a cause of action or\ndefense asserted in the action which has been assigned. The demand shall\nbe complied with within ten days of its service.\n</p>
        </content>
      </section>
